description: Provides a list of the first 100 RUNNABLE jobs associated to a single job queue.

parameters.name: jobQueue
parameters.description: The job queue's name or full queue Amazon Resource Name (ARN).

nested_items.name: frontOfQueue
nested_items.description: The list of the first 100 RUNNABLE jobs in each job queue. For first-in-first-out (FIFO) job queues, jobs are ordered based on their submission time. For fair-share scheduling (FSS) job queues, jobs are ordered based on their job priority and share usage.

nested_items.name: jobs
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Names (ARNs) of the first 100 RUNNABLE jobs in a named job queue. For first-in-first-out (FIFO) job queues, jobs are ordered based on their submission time. For fair-share scheduling (FSS) job queues, jobs are ordered based on their job priority and share usage.

nested_items.name: jobArn
nested_items.description: The ARN for a job in a named job queue.

nested_items.name: earliestTimeAtPosition
nested_items.description: The Unix timestamp (in milliseconds) for when the job transitioned to its current position in the job queue.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The Unix timestamp (in milliseconds) for when each of the first 100 RUNNABLE jobs were last updated.
